OL,4,G1850FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GMusical theatre lovers Lez and
OL,6,     GDerek hope to dazzle their guests
OL,7,     Gwith a showstopping stay. But
OL,8,     Gcutting comments about the
OL,9,     Gglassware and some surprisingly
OL,10,     Glow scores cause drama for the
OL,11,     Gduo.
OL,12,G1920FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe B&Bers visit The Greyhound
OL,14,     GHotel in Cromford, Derbyshire.
OL,15,     GTina and Danielle blow their
OL,16,     Gguests away with the comfy beds,
OL,17,     Gbut a trickle of traffic leads to
OL,18,     Gsome rude awakenings.
